  <brief_title>Evaluate the Effect of Osteo Introducer System in Total Hip Arthroplasty</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluate the Effect of Osteo Introducer System in Total Hip Arthroplasty: A Prospective, Multicenter, Randomized Controlled Study</official_title>
