  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Osteo introducer system is the instruments used in minimal invasive THA. This study will
      compare the minimal invasive THA using the osteo introducer system and THA using common
      instruments, to show the non-inferiority of osteo introducer system in safety and efficacy of
      THA surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
